nmap <C-Tab> <:buffer #>
nmap p <openFromClipboard>
nmap P <:tabnew><openFromClipboard>
nmap r <refreshTab>
nmap R <refreshTabWithoutCache>
nmap H <backInHistory>
nmap L <forwardInHistory>

" using g command
unmap g<C-a>
